      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;contact-cobra-boxing-and-fitness&#34;&gt;Contact Cobra Boxing and fitness&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Email: &lt;a href=&#34;mailto:cobraboxing73@gmail.com&#34;&gt;cobraboxing73@gmail.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;Phone: &lt;a href=&#34;tel:+447939470671&#34;&gt;07939 470671&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Address:&lt;br&gt;&#xA;Old Coop Building First Floor&lt;br&gt;&#xA;Walbottle, Hexham Rd&lt;br&gt;&#xA;Newcastle upon Tyne&lt;br&gt;&#xA;NE15 9SR&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Google Maps: &lt;a href=&#34;https://maps.app.goo.gl/TQDmhsbZmYTccw3Q9&#34;&gt;Open Cobra Gym location&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;If you are new to boxing, tell us your current fitness level and what you want to achieve. We will suggest the best class to start with.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
